350
00:24:27,020 --> 00:24:28,600
You can see it now.

351
00:24:28,600 --> 00:24:31,350
Yes. How lovely!

352
00:24:32,040 --> 00:24:35,279
So, this is the reason you asked for a hang out with me

353
00:24:35,280 --> 00:24:37,600
