362
00:25:02,900 --> 00:25:05,020
- You are her boss? 
 - Yeah.

363
00:25:07,280 --> 00:25:09,400
You are her boss?

364
00:25:09,400 --> 00:25:11,560
Yes, I am.

365
00:25:11,560 --> 00:25:14,699
This is obviously showing the differences between a buyer's show and a seller's show.

366
00:25:14,699 --> 00:25:20,000
Xiaoning described you to me as "steady, handsome, and not talkative."

367
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:23,300
I think I should bring her to check her brain or maybe her eyes first.

368
00:25:23,300 --> 00:25:25,940
What she described to you should be another person.

369
00:25:25,940 --> 00:25:28,299
An unimportant boss. All these are not important.

370
00:25:28,299 --> 00:25:31,879
The important point is that I've just come across her posts in Moments. And, you're here.

371
00:25:31,879 --> 00:25:34,860
Are we destined to meet each other?

372
00:25:34,860 --> 00:25:36,719
I'm done with my apologies. I'm leaving now.

373
00:25:36,719 --> 00:25:39,321
I will take good care of Jiang Xiaoning in the company.

374
00:25:39,321 --> 00:25:40,800
So?

375
00:25:40,800 --> 00:25:43,780
So, can you have a date with me?

376
00:25:43,780 --> 00:25:47,579
Is it so difficult to secure a job now? I even have to make an appointment for my best friend.

377
00:25:47,579 --> 00:25:51,419
- I just want to get to know more about you to see if it's possible for both of us... 
 - No.

378
00:25:55,700 --> 00:25:59,359
You didn't even give me a chance to start and you announced it's ended. That's quite hurtful.

379
00:26:02,300 --> 00:26:05,240
What do you like about me?

380
00:26:05,240 --> 00:26:09,700
I think that your shoulder throw is too amazing and charming.

381
00:26:09,700 --> 00:26:11,039
I think so.

382
00:26:11,040 --> 00:26:15,280
And also this smug face is really attractive to me.

383
00:26:18,800 --> 00:26:20,520
Were you born with a silver spoon?

384
00:26:21,940 --> 00:26:23,740
Kind of.

385
00:26:23,740 --> 00:26:25,439
That's a pity.

386
00:26:25,440 --> 00:26:27,739
I have no other talents.

387
00:26:27,739 --> 00:26:30,880
But I know my own background really well.

388
00:26:31,720 --> 00:26:35,579
I'm not suitable to marry into a rich family. And I don't want to be placed on a balance to be compared.

389
00:26:35,579 --> 00:26:38,059
So... In short,

390
00:26:38,059 --> 00:26:40,260
I'm allergic to a silver spoon.

391
00:26:41,460 --> 00:26:43,080
Oh, right.

392
00:26:43,080 --> 00:26:46,439
Especially someone like you. Bumming around all day.

393
00:26:46,439 --> 00:26:48,720
A silver spoon who lives like a bird.

394
00:26:50,580 --> 00:26:52,759
She got it all!

395
00:26:52,759 --> 00:26:55,120
She can see through me at a glance.

396
00:26:56,020 --> 00:27:00,700
She is adorable and charming even when she refuses me.

397
00:27:00,700 --> 00:27:03,420
I really like her!

