00:27:22,120 --> 00:27:23,900
Go ahead.

401
00:27:30,780 --> 00:27:33,979
It might be Director Xu. I'll go open the door.

402
00:27:38,240 --> 00:27:39,840
Wait!

403
00:27:45,100 --> 00:27:46,860
Boss.

