414
00:28:24,039 --> 00:28:26,780
And both of them were hugging each other.

415
00:28:27,940 --> 00:28:31,199
You miss your son a lot. You haven't seen him in a few years.

416
00:28:31,199 --> 00:28:33,799
That's just a hallucination. Are you going blind?

417
00:28:33,799 --> 00:28:35,999
I'm not. I saw it clearly.

418
00:28:35,999 --> 00:28:38,139
If you can see clearly, then open the door again

419
00:28:38,139 --> 00:28:41,619
