00:28:47,920 --> 00:28:52,299
This is the focus of the design plan. You must remember it. Okay?

422
00:28:54,160 --> 00:28:55,719
Son.

423
00:28:55,719 --> 00:28:59,640
Dad. Mom. When did you come in?

424
00:28:59,640 --> 00:29:01,600
We just came in.

425
00:29:03,020 --> 00:29:05,179
See, I told you that you have blurred vision.

426
00:29:05,179 --> 00:29:07,740
