459
00:30:59,199 --> 00:31:01,019
Yes. I'm done with work here.

460
00:31:01,019 --> 00:31:02,919
Uncle and Auntie, I'm leaving now.

461
00:31:02,919 --> 00:31:05,439
Don't. There are many dishes here. You should join us before you go.

462
00:31:05,439 --> 00:31:09,339
- Enjoy the meal. Enjoy the meal. 
 - Just join us before you leave.

463
00:31:10,120 --> 00:31:12,080
Xiao Chuan, you...

464
00:31:17,280 --> 00:31:18,760
 Oh no! 

465
00:31:18,760 --> 00:31:23,119
 I'm always unlucky. Would it cause the boss to be misunderstood? 

466
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:26,500
 It happened just by the time... 

467
00:31:31,220 --> 00:31:32,800
 Boss. 

468
00:31:43,240 --> 00:31:47,140
 This doesn't seem to be very unlucky. 

469
00:31:47,140 --> 00:31:48,539
 Jiang Xiaoning, 

470
00:31:48,539 --> 00:31:49,699
 what's wrong with you? 

471
00:31:49,699 --> 00:31:50,899
 Stop thinking too much. Back to work. 

472
00:31:55,600 --> 00:31:58,160
Come on, have some fruit.

473
00:32:00,040 --> 00:32:01,779
This little girl is great.

474
00:32:01,779 --> 00:32:03,919
She can cook at a young age.

475
00:32:03,920 --> 00:32:05,900
She cooks really well.

476
00:32:05,900 --> 00:32:08,219
Xiao Chuan, is this house cleaned by her?

477
00:32:08,219 --> 00:32:10,120
How clean this is!

478
00:32:10,120 --> 00:32:12,439
You have such a girlfriend who takes care of you by your side.

479
00:32:12,439 --> 00:32:14,980
Your father and I can rest assured.

480
00:32:14,980 --> 00:32:17,880
Mom, I am telling you once again.

481
00:32:17,880 --> 00:32:21,280
She's just my assistant, not my girlfriend.

482
00:32:23,380 --> 00:32:26,800
How long will you both stay here this time?

483
00:32:35,240 --> 00:32:37,260
Stay?

484
00:32:37,260 --> 00:32:40,380
We've been here for days, living in the hotel every day.

485
00:32:40,380 --> 00:32:42,180
That's no reason for us to stay.

486
00:32:42,180 --> 00:32:44,160
We're heading back tomorrow.

487
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:45,660
Gu.

488
00:32:57,320 --> 00:32:58,319
Son,

489
00:32:58,320 --> 00:32:59,799
regarding the matter that I told you about last time,

490
00:32:59,800 --> 00:33:01,980
what do you think of it?

491
00:33:01,980 --> 00:33:05,099
If you don't have any comments, your father and I

492
00:33:05,099 --> 00:33:06,519
will stay here for a few more days

493
00:33:06,519 --> 00:33:08,099
