500
00:33:20,000 --> 00:33:23,919
Over the past ten years, we never dare to speak badly to him.

501
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:25,199
We don't dare.

502
00:33:25,200 --> 00:33:27,499
Every word that we spoke to him was always

503
00:33:27,499 --> 00:33:28,819
after careful consideration.

504
00:33:28,819 --> 00:33:31,319
We were always afraid that our words might stimulate him.

505
00:33:31,320 --> 00:33:32,479
What about him?

506
00:33:32,480 --> 00:33:33,679
Everything was still fine in the past few years.

507
00:33:33,680 --> 00:33:35,540
But ever since he started his business, our relationship with him

508
00:33:35,540 --> 00:33:37,600
is getting more and more alienated.

509
00:33:37,600 --> 00:33:38,919
I have no idea about it.

510
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:42,140
Did we do something that offended him?

511
00:33:42,140 --> 00:33:44,800
Just stop.

512
00:33:48,140 --> 00:33:51,220
I've been keeping these words in my heart for a long time.

513
00:33:52,960 --> 00:33:55,800
I must ask him about that face to face today.

514
00:33:59,040 --> 00:34:02,779
Xiao Chuan, I'd like to ask you a question.

515
00:34:03,480 --> 00:34:06,280
You don't have to consider how I feel.

516
00:34:06,280 --> 00:34:11,020
Why do you treat your mom so indifferently?

517
00:34:11,020 --> 00:34:12,760
Why?

518
00:34:15,280 --> 00:34:17,900
I am used to being alone.

519
00:34:17,900 --> 00:34:20,480
I don't like people disturbing me.

520
00:34:21,280 --> 00:34:24,940
I am not used to it when there are many people at home.

521
00:34:24,940 --> 00:34:27,280
Please say it again.

522
00:34:30,679 --> 00:34:32,460
Xiao Chuan.

523
00:34:33,420 --> 00:34:34,940
Do you know?

524
00:34:34,940 --> 00:34:40,199
